[
  {
    "startTime": 0.227,
    "endTime": 2.31,
    "text": "If you watch my show, you know that I love pranks."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 2.31,
    "endTime": 5.220000000000001,
    "text": "I like scaring people, and I like making"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 5.22,
    "endTime": 6.57,
    "text": "celebrities wear an ear piece."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 6.57,
    "endTime": 7.9910000000000005,
    "text": "And I tell them to say things."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 7.991,
    "endTime": 9.99,
    "text": "And they can only do whatever I tell them to do."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 9.99,
    "endTime": 11.73,
    "text": "I love hiding Andy's phone and watching"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 11.73,
    "endTime": 13.350000000000001,
    "text": "him have a panic attack."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 13.35,
    "endTime": 16.2,
    "text": "And anyway, I know a great prank when I see one."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 16.2,
    "endTime": 18.9,
    "text": "And recently, I saw this tweet."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 18.9,
    "endTime": 20.32,
    "text": "These two friends made a huge poster of themselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 20.32,
    "endTime": 22.32,
    "text": "Hung it up at at a McDonald's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 22.32,
    "endTime": 25.29,
    "text": "And it stayed up there in the restaurant for two months."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 25.29,
    "endTime": 29.49,
    "text": "McDonald's had no idea until their tweet went viral."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 29.49,
    "endTime": 30.389,
    "text": "And I saw that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 30.39,
    "endTime": 31.89,
    "text": "And I was like, that's a good prank."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 31.89,
    "endTime": 32.71,
    "text": "Bring them to me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 32.71,
    "endTime": 34.35,
    "text": "So please welcome Jevh and Christian."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 34.35,
    "endTime": 36.34,
    "text": "First of all, congratulations."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.34,
    "endTime": 36.84,
    "text": "Thank you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 36.84,
    "endTime": 37.290000000000006,
    "text": "It's such an honor."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 37.29,
    "endTime": 38.588,
    "text": "That you got away with this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 38.588,
    "endTime": 39.902,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 39.902,
    "endTime": 41.22,
    "text": "It's crazy, trying to say."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.22,
    "endTime": 41.73,
    "text": "It is crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 41.73,
    "endTime": 43.513,
    "text": "So how did you come up with this idea?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 43.514,
    "endTime": 45.93,
    "text": "Oh well, Christian and I we actually go to that McDonald's"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 45.93,
    "endTime": 46.83,
    "text": "pretty often."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 46.83,
    "endTime": 49.769,
    "text": "And we sit in front of the wall where the picture's at."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 49.77,
    "endTime": 51.900000000000006,
    "text": "And we sit there pretty often."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 51.9,
    "endTime": 52.89,
    "text": "And we look up, and it's this blank wall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 52.89,
    "endTime": 53.39,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 53.39,
    "endTime": 55.910000000000004,
    "text": "So it's kind of like inviting us to put something on it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 55.91,
    "endTime": 57.69,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 57.69,
    "endTime": 58.48,
    "text": "We looked around."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 58.48,
    "endTime": 60.4,
    "text": "And we saw these other posters on there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 60.4,
    "endTime": 62.73,
    "text": "And we saw that there's different ethnicities."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 62.73,
    "endTime": 65.128,
    "text": "And we saw that they're all these people having fun."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 65.129,
    "endTime": 68.67,
    "text": "So we decide to represent ourselves as Asians"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 68.67,
    "endTime": 71.76,
    "text": "to be up there as well."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 71.76,
    "endTime": 74.7,
    "text": "So we decided to put it ourselves."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 74.7,
    "endTime": 75.119,
    "text": "And he always basically--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 75.12,
    "endTime": 79.42,
    "text": "I play tricks with my friends a lot, so this is crazy."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.42,
    "endTime": 79.92,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 79.92,
    "endTime": 83.38,
    "text": "He always gets crazy ideas like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 83.38,
    "endTime": 85.259,
    "text": "So you had to make the whole thing."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 85.26,
    "endTime": 86.47,
    "text": "You had to have it made."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 86.47,
    "endTime": 87.31,
    "text": "Yes, that's correct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.31,
    "endTime": 87.81,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 87.81,
    "endTime": 90.72,
    "text": "And let's talk about how you went about doing this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 90.72,
    "endTime": 92.99,
    "text": "All right, so you took pictures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 92.99,
    "endTime": 95.309,
    "text": "Yeah, we went to our neighborhood event center."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 95.31,
    "endTime": 98.46000000000001,
    "text": "We bought our own McDonald's food to take the picture from."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 98.46,
    "endTime": 100.886,
    "text": "And we wanted to make sure that it was like a stock image."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 100.886,
    "endTime": 101.759,
    "text": "Like it looked legit."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 101.76,
    "endTime": 102.26,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 102.26,
    "endTime": 105.807,
    "text": "And so we set up a tripod in front of our event center--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 105.807,
    "endTime": 106.89,
    "text": "neighborhood event center."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 106.89,
    "endTime": 109.8,
    "text": "And then we walked 10 feet away."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.8,
    "endTime": 109.99,
    "text": "We take pictures."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 109.99,
    "endTime": 111.955,
    "text": "And then we look back to see if it was good."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 111.956,
    "endTime": 112.83,
    "text": "And we kept doing it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 112.83,
    "endTime": 114.292,
    "text": "I mean, this cost you some money."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 114.292,
    "endTime": 115.42,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.42,
    "endTime": 115.92,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 115.92,
    "endTime": 118.22,
    "text": "So then, you're putting it in."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 118.22,
    "endTime": 120.605,
    "text": "And you had to make it look like other posters, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 120.605,
    "endTime": 121.23,
    "text": "That's correct."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.23,
    "endTime": 121.73,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 121.73,
    "endTime": 123.48,
    "text": "And then you had to--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 123.48,
    "endTime": 124.48,
    "text": "how did you put it up?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 124.48,
    "endTime": 127.44,
    "text": "You had to put fake McDonald's uniforms on."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 127.44,
    "endTime": 130.566,
    "text": "So that's pretty funny, Ellen."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 130.566,
    "endTime": 133.53,
    "text": "We went to-- I went to a neighborhood-- or a Goodwill"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 133.53,
    "endTime": 134.88,
    "text": "nearby with my friend."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 134.88,
    "endTime": 137.1,
    "text": "And he suggested I should go get a uniform,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 137.1,
    "endTime": 139.23,
    "text": "so I could dress the part."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 139.23,
    "endTime": 140.76899999999998,
    "text": "And I went back home."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 140.77,
    "endTime": 142.8,
    "text": "We edited a fake badge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 142.8,
    "endTime": 143.50900000000001,
    "text": "I throw in a tie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 143.509,
    "endTime": 144.7,
    "text": "Well, wait."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 144.8,
    "endTime": 146.22,
    "text": "They just have McDonald's uniforms for sale anywhere?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.22,
    "endTime": 146.99,
    "text": "Yeah, in Goodwill."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 146.99,
    "endTime": 147.36,
    "text": "It was weird."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 147.36,
    "endTime": 149.10000000000002,
    "text": "It was the first location we went to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 149.1,
    "endTime": 151.57,
    "text": "And it was the right size for me too."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 151.57,
    "endTime": 152.625,
    "text": "So it was meant to be."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 152.625,
    "endTime": 153.125,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 153.125,
    "endTime": 154.2,
    "text": "It sure was."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 154.2,
    "endTime": 155.10999999999999,
    "text": "It was calling him."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 155.11,
    "endTime": 156.36,
    "text": "Yeah, it was legit calling me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 156.36,
    "endTime": 159.66000000000003,
    "text": "And we went back to my house."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 159.66,
    "endTime": 160.799,
    "text": "We made a fake badge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 160.8,
    "endTime": 162.235,
    "text": "Regional Interior Coordinator."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 162.235,
    "endTime": 163.235,
    "text": "Yeah, I've made that up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 163.235,
    "endTime": 164.25,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.25,
    "endTime": 164.91,
    "text": "I don't know--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 164.91,
    "endTime": 166.1,
    "text": "Is that a position?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 166.1,
    "endTime": 167.281,
    "text": "It should be now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.282,
    "endTime": 167.99,
    "text": "It should be now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 167.99,
    "endTime": 169.59900000000002,
    "text": "It sounds pretty real."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 169.599,
    "endTime": 170.64,
    "text": "You already have a badge."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 170.64,
    "endTime": 172.45,
    "text": "Maybe that's what you could be there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.45,
    "endTime": 172.95,
    "text": "OK."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 172.95,
    "endTime": 174.48,
    "text": "So then let's show it going up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 174.48,
    "endTime": 176.16,
    "text": "Because you had to sneak this up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 176.16,
    "endTime": 178.62,
    "text": "And so the whole-- the restaurant's open, obviously."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 178.62,
    "endTime": 180.72,
    "text": "You walk in there with this giant poster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 180.72,
    "endTime": 182.62,
    "text": "Nobody's asking any questions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 182.62,
    "endTime": 183.12,
    "text": "Nope."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 183.12,
    "endTime": 184.23000000000002,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 184.23,
    "endTime": 186.84,
    "text": "And then you were careful, because you"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 186.84,
    "endTime": 187.5,
    "text": "put a certain kind of double stick"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 187.5,
    "endTime": 189.84,
    "text": "on it so you wouldn't damage the wall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 189.84,
    "endTime": 190.541,
    "text": "Yeah, we put adhesives in the back."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 190.541,
    "endTime": 192.21,
    "text": "Because if it was to get caught, then we"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 192.21,
    "endTime": 194.58,
    "text": "didn't want to make any trouble and have them take it down"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 194.58,
    "endTime": 195.21,
    "text": "if they want to."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 195.21,
    "endTime": 196.47,
    "text": "And make no damage to McDonald's whatsoever."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 196.47,
    "endTime": 197.1,
    "text": "Right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 197.1,
    "endTime": 198.35899999999998,
    "text": "Because then that would have been vandalism."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.36,
    "endTime": 198.75,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 198.75,
    "endTime": 200.76,
    "text": "I don't want to be accused for something like that."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 200.76,
    "endTime": 201.26,
    "text": "No."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 201.26,
    "endTime": 203.51899999999998,
    "text": "So you just-- all you did was put a poster up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 203.52,
    "endTime": 205.52,
    "text": "And it was up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 205.52,
    "endTime": 206.87,
    "text": "You must have been so nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 206.87,
    "endTime": 208.37,
    "text": "Yeah we were really nervous."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 208.37,
    "endTime": 210.23000000000002,
    "text": "Not as nervous as we are right now."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.23,
    "endTime": 210.73,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 210.73,
    "endTime": 212.88,
    "text": "We were lucky, because there's security cameras that are"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 212.88,
    "endTime": 213.81,
    "text": "facing different directions."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 213.81,
    "endTime": 216.31,
    "text": "But that wall, in particular, there was no security cameras."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 216.31,
    "endTime": 217.241,
    "text": "Conveniently."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 217.241,
    "endTime": 218.74,
    "text": "No one cares about that wall anyway."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 218.74,
    "endTime": 221.5,
    "text": "There were no security cameras protecting it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 221.5,
    "endTime": 222.5,
    "text": "And it needed something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 222.5,
    "endTime": 224.7,
    "text": "It was an empty wall."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.7,
    "endTime": 224.61999999999998,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 224.62,
    "endTime": 227.42000000000002,
    "text": "And now, do you still go back to that McDonald's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 227.42,
    "endTime": 228.75,
    "text": "And did people recognize you, like you're"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 228.75,
    "endTime": 229.83,
    "text": "models or something?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 229.83,
    "endTime": 231.24,
    "text": "When I first went there, I went with my mom."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 231.24,
    "endTime": 233.46,
    "text": "And I was scared that the employee would notice me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 233.46,
    "endTime": 235.751,
    "text": "So I told my mom to go run over there and order for me,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 235.751,
    "endTime": 237.57,
    "text": "while I hide in the corner or something."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 237.57,
    "endTime": 238.31,
    "text": "Hide in a booth."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 238.31,
    "endTime": 239.56,
    "text": "Your mother knew you did this?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 239.56,
    "endTime": 240.37,
    "text": "Yeah, she did."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.37,
    "endTime": 240.87,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 240.87,
    "endTime": 242.67000000000002,
    "text": "She was not for it at first."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 242.67,
    "endTime": 244.48,
    "text": "But then whenever I told her about it"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 244.48,
    "endTime": 245.82,
    "text": "and when the poster came--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 245.82,
    "endTime": 248.214,
    "text": "I didn't tell her I bought it and shipped it over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 248.214,
    "endTime": 250.38,
    "text": "But when it came to my house, and she saw in person,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 250.38,
    "endTime": 252.46,
    "text": "she couldn't help but laugh with my dad."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 252.46,
    "endTime": 254.459,
    "text": "First of all, I can't believe no one noticed that,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 254.46,
    "endTime": 256.67,
    "text": "and it stayed up for two months."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 256.67,
    "endTime": 259.42,
    "text": "And then, have you heard from McDonald's?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 259.42,
    "endTime": 260.1,
    "text": "Yes, actually."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 260.1,
    "endTime": 262.56,
    "text": "Me and my friends visited that McDonald's location."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 262.56,
    "endTime": 263.88,
    "text": "And we decided to eat."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 263.88,
    "endTime": 265.11,
    "text": "And then, they called us."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 265.11,
    "endTime": 266.97,
    "text": "It was about a week ago."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 266.97,
    "endTime": 269.32000000000005,
    "text": "And they talked about--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 269.32,
    "endTime": 271.29,
    "text": "as soon as they called-- it was Chris Stanley."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 271.29,
    "endTime": 272.67,
    "text": "He works for corporate."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 272.67,
    "endTime": 273.3,
    "text": "He called me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 273.3,
    "endTime": 276.11,
    "text": "And as soon as he answered-- or I answered,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 276.11,
    "endTime": 279.997,
    "text": "I asked him if I was going to get in trouble."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 279.997,
    "endTime": 281.58000000000004,
    "text": "Because I didn't know if I was or not."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 281.58,
    "endTime": 282.75,
    "text": "And I wanted to make sure I wasn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 282.75,
    "endTime": 283.97,
    "text": "And he said that I wasn't."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 283.97,
    "endTime": 286.46000000000004,
    "text": "So that's all that matters."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 286.46,
    "endTime": 287.29999999999995,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 287.3,
    "endTime": 290.454,
    "text": "And when he told me, I was like--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 290.454,
    "endTime": 291.87,
    "text": "because there was an event, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 291.87,
    "endTime": 292.37,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 292.37,
    "endTime": 294.12,
    "text": "There is an event that was planned."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 294.12,
    "endTime": 295.812,
    "text": "And he invited both of us to go over"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 295.812,
    "endTime": 297.2,
    "text": "to the event at the location."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.2,
    "endTime": 297.52,
    "text": "At that restaurant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 297.52,
    "endTime": 298.289,
    "text": "Yeah."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 298.29,
    "endTime": 300.63,
    "text": "And when he told me, I was like, maybe this is a trap."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 300.63,
    "endTime": 301.706,
    "text": "And maybe cops are going to be there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 301.706,
    "endTime": 302.956,
    "text": "There's going to be handcuffs."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 302.956,
    "endTime": 304.12,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.12,
    "endTime": 304.77,
    "text": "But no."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 304.77,
    "endTime": 308.549,
    "text": "The event was actually a great thing to happened."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 308.55,
    "endTime": 310.89,
    "text": "They invited us to go over there."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 310.89,
    "endTime": 313.272,
    "text": "They're going to actually take down the poster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 313.272,
    "endTime": 315.48,
    "text": "But they're going to renovate their whole restaurant."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 315.48,
    "endTime": 318.44,
    "text": "The renovation was planned months before the poster."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 318.44,
    "endTime": 319.89,
    "text": "Before this whole idea came up."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 319.89,
    "endTime": 321.757,
    "text": "To show much more diversity, which is--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 321.757,
    "endTime": 323.59000000000003,
    "text": "this is what you brought to their attention."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 323.59,
    "endTime": 326.39,
    "text": "And Crazy Rich Asians was a really big influence on me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 326.4,
    "endTime": 327.15,
    "text": "It really pushed me over."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 327.15,
    "endTime": 328.5,
    "text": "Because I watched the movie three times."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 328.5,
    "endTime": 329.13,
    "text": "It's insane."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 329.13,
    "endTime": 331.4,
    "text": "So we wanted to be like crazy middle class."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 331.4,
    "endTime": 333.854,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 336.12,
    "endTime": 337.14,
    "text": "That's the next movie."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 337.14,
    "endTime": 338.57,
    "text": "Crazy Middle-Class Asians."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 338.57,
    "endTime": 340.305,
    "text": "We're the stars."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 340.305,
    "endTime": 342.28000000000003,
    "text": "Or maybe lower middle class."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 342.28,
    "endTime": 345.501,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 345.501,
    "endTime": 346.0,
    "text": "All right."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 346.0,
    "endTime": 348.75,
    "text": "I have a couple of surprises for you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 348.75,
    "endTime": 350.83,
    "text": "We, first of all--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 350.83,
    "endTime": 353.169,
    "text": "here's our billboard outside."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 353.17,
    "endTime": 354.34000000000003,
    "text": "This is me."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 354.34,
    "endTime": 355.311,
    "text": "And then we did this."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 355.312,
    "endTime": 358.85,
    "text": "[LAUGHTER]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 358.85,
    "endTime": 360.76000000000005,
    "text": "We're loving it."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 360.76,
    "endTime": 364.0,
    "text": "So second, I want you to try to sneak this into another"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 364.0,
    "endTime": 364.73,
    "text": "McDonald's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 368.915,
    "endTime": 369.845,
    "text": "Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 369.845,
    "endTime": 371.48,
    "text": "This is some fan art."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 371.48,
    "endTime": 374.39000000000004,
    "text": "A viewer named Tom sent this to me over the summer."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 374.39,
    "endTime": 376.88,
    "text": "And I shouldn't keep this for myself."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 376.88,
    "endTime": 378.13,
    "text": "This should go somewhere else."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 378.13,
    "endTime": 380.57,
    "text": "So you're going to sneak that into a McDonald's."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 380.57,
    "endTime": 381.59,
    "text": "All right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 381.59,
    "endTime": 384.65,
    "text": "And finally, McDonald's loves customers like you."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 384.65,
    "endTime": 386.15,
    "text": "And they're committed to diversity"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 386.15,
    "endTime": 387.899,
    "text": "and want to represent all their customers,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 387.899,
    "endTime": 391.435,
    "text": "so they're going to use the two of you in a marketing campaign."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 391.435,
    "endTime": 393.375,
    "text": "And since--"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 393.375,
    "endTime": 396.77,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 401.135,
    "endTime": 402.75,
    "text": "Are you sure?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 402.75,
    "endTime": 403.75,
    "text": "This can't be happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 403.75,
    "endTime": 404.75,
    "text": "This can't be happening."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 404.75,
    "endTime": 406.92,
    "text": "Not only that, but since you're in a campaign,"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 406.92,
    "endTime": 408.15000000000003,
    "text": "they need to pay you, right?"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 408.15,
    "endTime": 410.09999999999997,
    "text": "So you're each getting a check for $25,000."
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.1,
    "endTime": 410.90900000000005,
    "text": "Ooh!"
  },
  {
    "startTime": 410.91,
    "endTime": 414.56,
    "text": "[APPLAUSE]"
  }
]